column1: write a python script for me to load youtube and search dota2 on Android simulator using appuim
column2:
from appium import webdriver

desired_caps = {
    'platformName': 'Android',
    'deviceName': 'Android Emulator',
    'appPackage': 'com.google.android.youtube',
    'appActivity': 'com.google.android.apps.youtube.app.WatchWhileActivity'
}

driver = webdriver.Remote('http://localhost:4723/wd/hub', desired_caps)

# Search for Dota2
search_field = driver.find_element_by_id('com.google.android.youtube:id/search_edit_text')
search_field.send_keys('Dota2')

# Click on the search button
search_button = driver.find_element_by_id('com.google.android.youtube:id/search_button')
search_button.click()

from appium import webdriver

desired_caps = {
    'platformName': 'Android',
    'deviceName': 'Android Emulator',
    'appPackage': 'com.google.android.youtube',
    'appActivity': 'com.google.android.apps.youtube.app.WatchWhileActivity'
}

driver = webdriver.Remote('http://localhost:4723/wd/hub', desired_caps)

# Click on the search button

search_button.click()
